              "x": "Cognitive behavioral therapy is effective in treating a wide range of mental health conditions, including obsessive-compulsive disorder (OCD) and post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD)."
            },
            {
              "cf": "",
              "x": "During cognitive behavioral therapy sessions, clients learn to challenge irrational beliefs and replace them with more realistic and positive ones."
            },
            {
